# Prework - CodePathProject
Submitted by: Christopher Yoeurng
CodePathProject is an app that allows you to change the color of the background by pressing a button and allows you to choose whether or not you want blue to be included in the calculation of that color. 

Time spent: **1** hours spent in total

## Required Features

The following **required** functionality is completed:

- [x] Users are see a screen with three labels and a button
- [x] Tapping the button changes the screen color to a random color
 
